snippet.title: Let's Play Strawberry Jam [1] Meadowvalley
snippet.description:
Daniel Remar's most recent game (not to be confused with Daniel Linssen) is a platforming text adventure released just in October of last year. It's currently only chapter one of hopefully many. You can even play it yourself!
http://www.remar.se/daniel/strawberry.php
